t the data, just read the memory!  It could be fast memory, slow memory, on chip, off chip, etc.%0a%3c %0a%3c Temperature might need to be stabilized or compensated for.%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Atmospheric noise%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
